storyInfo: Carnelian intentionally avoids revealing her true colors to her sister, but with spies snooping on the Count following her everywhere, she must also deal with them quickly.

attributes.content: Kal'tsit? Are you listening?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: The last treatment worked very well. Count Hohenlohe has gotten much better. Thank you for your help.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Oh, wait a moment.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: I don't recommend letting yourself get distracted in battle.
attributes.name: Kal'tsit

attributes.content: This is hardly a battle. Don't worry. It'll be over soon.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Back on topic... I will be staying a little longer than usual at Rhodes Island this time. That won't be a problem, will it?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Rhodes Island will never turn away its operators.
attributes.name: Kal'tsit

attributes.content: You can get to the point and say I'm welcome.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: If that's what you want to hear, you're welcome here.
attributes.name: Kal'tsit

attributes.content: Right... makes me wonder if I should say you're straight to the point or beating around the bush.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Whatever. Let us talk about the next treatment, then.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Medical will formulate the medicine used in the next treatment based on the physical examination data you provided. This will take some time, but not too long.
attributes.name: Kal'tsit

attributes.content: I still insist that the Count receive regular, detailed examinations. That's the only way we can plan out his treatment effectively.
attributes.name: Kal'tsit

attributes.content: Best if I bring him to you for a checkup, right?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Considering the Count's position, that is far too risky. Too bad. Things could have been so much simpler if certain people were less stubborn.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: In any case, until the medicine's formulated, I will be working alongside Ankhesena... the little squirt. I trust you'll have no problem with that?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: You are free to do as you please.
attributes.name: Kal'tsit

attributes.content: Wonderful, then.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Ah, right. One more thing...
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Looks like some pests managed to follow our tracks. The Count is a popular man, and even a lowly attendant like me gets followed.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: But don't worry. This won't affect Rhodes Island whatsoever. I'll take care of it.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Okay, let me think. What should I do with you?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Instead of Rhodes Island's gentle way of doing things, I'm much better at silencing people directly... It makes things much easier for everyone.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: W-What are you doing?!
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: Why are you shaking? If you chose to be a robber, surely you must've been prepared for this to happen one day?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Relax, the pain will stop in no timeâ€”
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Sis, I'm done with my part.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Sis?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Ankhesena, what are you doing here? Have you taken off all the guys on your side?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Mhm.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: The Medic Operators are treating the injured, and I helped by bringing them medicine.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Good job.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: It was nothing.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: What are you doing?
attributes.name: Beeswax
Carnelian
attributes.content: Oh, nothing special...

attributes.name: Carnelian
attributes.content: Just having a friendly chat with the nice men here.
(The bitch's lying!)
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: (Friendly chat my ass!)
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: *cough*.
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: Friendly... chat?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Friendly chat!
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Mm, okay...
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Hello?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: You talking to us?
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Yep. After that lesson, you know how awesome we are, don't you?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: So please stop trying to bother the Pioneer Team. They are very hardworking people, and please find an honest job.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Huh? Work? What are you talking about, you punk ass...
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: (Hm? You want to repeat that?)
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Urk...
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: (Shut up, idiot!)
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: (Ow! What are you smacking me for...?)
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: D-Don't worry! We definitely won't ever look for no trouble with the Pioneer Team ever again. We... We will work the hardest we can!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: ...Really?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Of course. Of course! We've learned our lesson, much thanks to you two!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Your word's not worth much.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Okay, that's good to hear.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Ankhesena?!
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Are you sure about this?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Hmm... Is that not good enough?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Let me think...
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: No, we'll handle this your way. I'll always support your decisions.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: The short-haired Caprinae pauses for a moment and turns her gaze from her younger sister to the bandits beside her. Though her eyes sweep past them only very briefly, it's evident they are blood-colored, cold, and harsh.
Sis? What's wrong?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Hm? Oh.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: It's nothing. If this is taken care of, then let's go back.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: ...Okay.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Wow, they actually left.
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: What do we do, Boss? Are we really gonna do honest work?
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: W-What kind of work can we do?
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: Work? Work your ass!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Now hurry and get everyone up! We're leaving!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Alright, alright! Sheesh, why smack me again...?
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: Okay, this should do it for now.
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: Your injuries aren't very serious, but you should try to avoid any intense physical labor for a while and let your body rest as much as you can.
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: But if we don't hurry up and finish the construction, those bandits will...
attributes.name: Injured Pioneer

attributes.content: Alright! Don't worry about it. We'll figure it out somehow.
attributes.name: Strong Pioneer

attributes.content: Don't worry, Doc. We'll keep an eye on our wounded and make sure they rest up!
attributes.name: Strong Pioneer

attributes.content: Are you finished treating the injured?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: I taught those bandits a lesson with Ankhesena... Beeswax. Is there anything else we can help you with?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Carnelian! Thank you so much for escorting me here!
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: I'm finished with the Pioneers' treatment. Their injuries aren't serious, and even the Infected among them aren't in particularly dire condition.
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: The mission itself can be called a success, but...
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: You're worried about the bandits?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Yes...
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: They have been operating here for a while now. It doesn't look like they'll stop just because you teach them a lesson or two.
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: And we're only here on a mission. Can't always help out... can we?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: *sigh*... Everyone can tell at a glance there is nothing we can do about those men, but that little squirt still has no idea.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: How worrying.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Haha... Beeswax is working very hard already, though! The first time we went on a mission together, she got so lost that she didn't make her way back to the campsite until the morning on the third day...
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: Oh? She didn't tell me that one. Maybe I could take you out to dinner one day and hear the whole story?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: I would love to, if we get the chance! I want to show you the specialties we have on offer at the Rhodes Island canteen, too!
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: Speaking of which, where is Beeswax?
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: She said she's got something to do by herself.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Huh? By herself?! S-She's not going to get lost again, is she...?
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: I'm a little surprised, though. I thought you would be so worried that you would follow her.
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: If I try to have a hand in everything, she'll never grow up.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Ankhesena is out here to gain experience; it's not so bad to let her experience more by herself. Guardians who keep kids on a tight leash will only find themselves hatedâ€”That said, I'm worried, of course.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: That's why... if you don't mind, is it okay if I take charge of this bandit problem?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Do you have a good way to solve this? If there's anything I can do, I can...
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: Thanks, but there's no need.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Most Rhodes Islanders might find my methods a little... strange.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: W-What do you mean by that...?
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: Hah hah, don't worry about it. Just leave it to me.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: At first, joining Rhodes Island was only a stopgap measure.
The young Count is afflicted with a disgraceful disease and must mix with Leithanien's upper crust while hiding his identity as an Infected.
He is still a boy, but his demeanor is already like that of a seasoned veteran.
But in Carnelian's eyes, instead of a dignified image, he instead reminds her of a young, seriously injured beast who had lost its parents that she once saw.
Confronted by hunters, it bared its fangs and raised its hackles, feigning the last bit of dignity it could manage as a wild beast.
In the beginning, that was the only reason why she chose to stick her nose into that.
And the agreement she signed with Rhodes Island was but one of the many insignificant things she had no choice but to do at the time.
Hey, what are you strolling out here at this hour for?
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: My head hurts so bad I can't sleep. Ugh, what a ruthless bitch...
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: We made this trip all for nothing, thanks to that wretched woman.
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: As soon as those Rhodes Island busybodies leave, we're going to teach that Pioneer Team a real lesson! See if they still dare toâ€”
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Dare to what?
Who goes there?!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Good evening, gentlemen.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: It sounds like you're having an interesting conversation. Mind if I join?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: You... You're the crazy bitch from this afternoon!
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: My, how rude.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: But fine. This is actually just perfect. If you got polite all of a sudden, I might not be able to bring myself to do this.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: W-What are you going to do?!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Y-You promised us you'd let us go this afternoon...
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Hmm? Did I?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: I did say I'd support Ankhesena's decision, but let you go?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Peculiar. Did I ever say that?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: You stinkin' bitch!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Oh, don't get yourselves so worked up, gentlemen.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Your profanities won't save you, but before I deal with you, I have a little question.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: What is it?
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: We'll give you an answer, but we need your word that you won't kill us.
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Urgh!!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Sorry, but I'm not here to discuss terms.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: It seems you don't quite understand the situation you are in. I shouldn't have been so lenient on you in the daylight.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: My hand! No, please! I'll tell you anything. Please let me go!
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Very wellâ€”
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Wait!
(...Again?!)
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Ugh.
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Carnelian! We finally caught up to you...
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: Sis, wait. Don't hurt them.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: *cough*, Ankhesena, listen to me. This is just a misunderstanding. I'm having a happy little chat with these gentlemen...
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Sis.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: I'm not stupid.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: I know the way you fight. You don't have to hide it from me.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: The elders all told me when you went hunting for the first time, you came back completely drenched in blood, and your prey was in tatters.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: You're way too direct and rough with how you handle things!
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: The elders tell you everything, huh?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Okay, I'll stop... but what do you plan on doing with them?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: You shouldn't expect them to go get jobs after you free them, and if you leave them be, who knows what they'll do in the future... We won't be staying here forever.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Yes, I know that.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: But, Sis, this is Columbia.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: You mean...?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Maybe we should follow Columbia's rules.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Hehe, Beeswax's really thought of everything. She went into the city by herself this afternoon just to take care of this.
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: Police. Sorry we got here late.
attributes.name: Columbian Police

attributes.content: Are these the bandits that attacked the Pioneer Team on multiple occasions and have been assaulting passersby in the area that you mentioned?
attributes.name: Columbian Police

attributes.content: Shit... It had to be these cops...
attributes.name: Shrewd Bandit

attributes.content: Hmph, you degenerates, huh?
attributes.name: Columbian Police

attributes.content: There's more, too! Officer, please come with me!
attributes.name: Medic Operator

attributes.content: I asked the Pioneer Team. These men have done plenty of bad things here before this. If they're caught, they probably won't get to come back for a while.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Now they can't do anything bad anymore.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Well... I'm surprised you thought of this.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Back home, we wouldn't even begin to think about talking to the police, but the Doctor says I have to learn to follow the local customs wherever I go.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: And we have to borrow all the strength we can... The Doctor taught me that, too.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: I see, so the Doctor taught you...
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Hahah.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Ankhesena.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Do you like Rhodes Island?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Yep...
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: I sure do.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Is it okay if I ask why?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: There are lots of kind people at Rhodes Island. If I stay there, I can see a lot more things that I haven't seen and learn lots of new stuff.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Isn't that what we came out into the world to do?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: You're right.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: It's true. Those traditions exist so we have a chance to understand the outside world, to absorb knowledge that we're interested in, and to see things that we've never seen.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: That's how I made it all the way here, and now it's your turn, Ankhesena.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Yes... I understand that well.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Sis? What's wrong? Are you... Are you sad?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: No. I'm actually very happy.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Who would've thought that the little squirt who clung to my leg all those years ago would say something that makes so much sense? Oh, how time flies.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: I'm a little sad I couldn't see how you grow so dependable, though.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Yep, I guess I'll have a chat with the Doctor sometime. I'm sure I'll learn lots of interesting things about you.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Sis!
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Haha, I'll stop teasing you.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: You did very well. I'm glad you know how to solve the challenges you face, your own way.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: What I said still stands. It doesn't matter what you want to do. I'll always support your decisions. So don't be afraid, no matter what comes your way. Just do as you will.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Right, I understand.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: You're going to leave soon, right?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Sorry... I can't always be there with you.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: It's okay.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: It's fine. While you're gone, I'll keep traveling with Rhodes Island. I still have lots to learn...
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: I want to become even more dependable, so I can help you next time.
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Phew, now I can rest easy, knowing you'll be fine at Rhodes Island.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Even if something unexpected happens on that end, you won't be in danger here.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Sis...?
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: You never let me in on the dangerous stuff you're doing! You big dummy!
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Oh? Finally going to sulk?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: (Pouts)
attributes.name: Beeswax

attributes.content: Okay, don't be mad. Just like you're starting to discover your own way of doing things, I'm sure you know...
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: I have my ways, too.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Rhodes Island accepts people of all kinds. Some came together because of how like-minded they are, but even more of them, like her, opted to stay a while for all kinds of reasons.

From the bottom of her heart, Carnelian feels truly gratified, knowing that Ankhesena has been able to broaden her horizons, learn to think for herself, as well as understand and accept Rhodes Island's ideals.
Even though she herself only follows her heart, Carnelian thinks that, perhaps while she's around all these adorable Rhodes Islanders, she should restrain herself a little and work with them.
If she hangs around them long enough, perhaps she too will be influenced by them and become softer?
That's something to look forward to, but before that...
(No mistake. That Caprinae woman is Count Hohenlohe's attendant.)
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: (Someone so close to a Leithanian count is secretly in close contact with an Oripathy-related pharmaceutical company...)
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: (Rhodes Island, huh... Feels like I've heard that name before.)
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: (Anyway, I gotta get word about this toâ€”)
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: Good evening again, vermin.
Y-You're the attendantâ€”
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: Shh.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Guh...!
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: That's a great disguise. You almost fooled me.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Those nobles really don't mind all the trouble, do they? They're even sending men to keep an eye on a lowly servant like me.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: It took me quite a bit of work to sneak over here behind Ankhesena's back. She's not so easy to fool anymore.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: *cough*... You... I knew it... You're...
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: Infectâ€”
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: Silence is golden, sir.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: *cough*, ahhâ€”!! My leg!
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: Oh, I'm sorry. Did that hurt?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Come, tell me who's behind all this, and I'll send you on your merry way. How about it?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: It's ironic how many vicious methods those civilized men came up with. I'm not very used to them, but if you're so stubborn, I have no choice but to give them a try.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: I guess you wouldn't want to try them out, though?
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Ugh... Ah... Ahh...!
attributes.name: Vulgar Bandit

attributes.content: This should do for now.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: I need to report the situation to the Count as soon as possible. Kids these days really are tough to deal with.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Right... If I don't head back soon, Ankhesena will probably get suspicious. She was a sharp girl to begin with, but she wasn't this clever. I wonder who she picked that up from.
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: *sigh*... Kids really do grow up so fast...
attributes.name: Carnelian

attributes.content: Well, seems I'll be going back in shame if I don't work a little harder.
attributes.name: Carnelian
